Hadrian Personal Use and Educational License (PUEL)
===================================================

This license applies if you download the Hadrian Scoring Engine either as a JAR
file (binary) or source code (ASCII) from the Downloads page. It does not apply
to the PFA specification, which is licensed by the Data Mining Group (DMG).
In summary, the Hadrian PUEL allows you to use the Hadrian Scoring Engine free
of charge

  * for personal use,
  * for product evaluation, or 
  * for academic use

The Hadrian PUEL does not allow you to use the Hadrian Scoring Engine for any
commercial use.

